name: Toronto Cinematica - Cinestill Film at Night

metadata.name: Craving Neon
metadata.description:
Exploring the snowy Toronto streets with my Pentax 67, I came across the pink neon of Blondies Pizza. A great local pizza joint with a perfect neon sign. 


Shot on Cinestill 800T 120 film and a Pentax 6x7.
Collector will receive a high quality art print.
